175 A.3d 152 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. GLENROY A. DEER, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-259 September Term 2017

079932 October 26, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000430-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
